{
  "text": "According to existing research on environmental governance, systems that embrace adaptive governance are more resilient to climate change than other systems because they are more capable to handle uncertainty (cf. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
  "correct_citation": {
